OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774534302
OL,3,CSynagogue offers #2,000 reward after
OL,4,C'devastating' theft of sacred scrolls
OL,6,FA Jewish community has been left
OL,7,F"devastated" after thieves broke into
OL,8,Fa synagogue and stole a heavy safe
OL,9,Fcontaining two sacred scrolls.
OL,11,FThe Beis HaMedrash Torah Etz Chaim,
OL,12,Flocated on Bury New Road in Salford
OL,13,Fand known locally as "the 69," has now
OL,14,Flaunched an urgent campaign to recover
OL,15,Fthe items, offering a #2,000 reward
OL,16,Ffor their safe return.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
