PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774534302
OL,3,CSynagogue offers #2,000 reward after
OL,4,C'devastating' theft of sacred scrolls
OL,6,FCCTV footage from the incident, which
OL,7,Foccurred at approximately 5.30am on
OL,8,FFriday, 20 March, shows three men
OL,9,Fdressed in hi-vis clothing entering
OL,10,Fthe building.
OL,12,FThe trio spent 33 minutes inside the
OL,13,Fsynagogue, eventually loading a "very,
OL,14,Fvery heavy" safe into a waiting van.
OL,16,FA committee member for the synagogue
OL,17,Fsaid: "It looks like they knew where
OL,18,Fthey were going. They went upstairs...
OL,19,Fthey did some damage on the walls and
OL,20,Fthe floor."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
