OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774534302
OL,3,CSynagogue offers #2,000 reward after
OL,4,C'devastating' theft of sacred scrolls
OL,6,FThe only contents of the safe were two
OL,7,FSefer Torahs which are handwritten
OL,8,Fscrolls produced on parchment by
OL,9,Fhighly trained scribes using special
OL,10,Fink.
OL,12,FMembers of the shul have expressed
OL,13,Fdeep concern that the thieves will
OL,14,F"disrespect" the sacred scrolls as
OL,15,Fthey have no resale value to the
OL,16,Fgeneral public.
OL,18,FUsed weekly at synagogues, they are
OL,19,Fpassed down from generation to
OL,20,Fgeneration and were between 50 and 100
OL,21,Fyears old.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774534302
OL,3,CSynagogue offers #2,000 reward after
OL,4,C'devastating' theft of sacred scrolls
OL,6,F"It's very devastating news and it's
OL,7,Freally difficult on us," one member
OL,8,Fsaid. "I think they'll be devastated
OL,9,Fwith what they find. For them, it's
OL,10,Fnot worth even a penny. You can't sell
OL,11,Fthese things."
OL,13,FThe community is pleading for the
OL,14,Fitems to be handled with care.
OL,16,F"We are very scared, we don't want
OL,17,Fthem to handle it with disrespect," a
OL,18,Fmember added. "You can't chuck it in
OL,19,Fthe bin, the floor, and you can't burn
OL,20,Fthese things."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
