PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774534302
OL,3,CSynagogue offers #2,000 reward after
OL,4,C'devastating' theft of sacred scrolls
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed it
OL,7,Fis investigating the burglary. A
OL,8,Fspokesperson stated: "Officers are
OL,9,Faware of this, no arrests have been
OL,10,Fmade at this time and it is being
OL,11,Finvestigated."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
